sentence.text: Using data from the Women's Circle of Health Study (WCHS) of 1,307 European-American (EA) and 1,365 African-American (AA) breast cancer cases and controls, we aimed to replicate 53 earlier GWAS variants for AM and negative regulation of muscle contraction in AA and EA groups and to perform analyses on total and net reproductive lifespan (TRLS; NRLS).
